    "body": "Thanks for the report. Just to be clear this doesn't have anything to do with the IPython rendering. AFAICT if both the index and columns are MultiIndex and you use `index=False` in `to_html` the column headers of the output seem misaligned.\r\n\r\nInvestigation and PRs welcome"
